vAlign=3D"top">=0A<P class=3DMsoNormal>The Amon'krie are small wo=
rm-like beings just under 2 meters long. They propel their bodies=
 by undulating their underside.<SPAN style=3D"mso-spacerun: yes">=
&nbsp; </SPAN>They have several small tubules near their head whi=
ch they use to grasp tools. They prefer to make their homes under=
 the&nbsp;ice of a planet and have very poor eyesight. Their aver=
age lifespan is about 50 years.</P>=0A<P class=3DMsoNormal><O:P><=
/O:P></P>=0A<P class=3DMsoNormal>The Amon'krie have a society mad=
e up of several groups of governing personnel. Each group has abs=
olute authority over a different sector of their government.</P>=0A=
<P class=3DMsoNormal><O:P></O:P></P>=0A<P class=3DMsoNormal>They=20=
work together in a delicate network of checks and balances. Their=
 society is strongly xenophobic and does not interact well with o=
ther races. <SPAN style=3D"mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>The A=
mon'krie are thought to have evolved on a planet far on the rim o=
f the galaxy. </P>=0A<P class=3DMsoNormal><O:P></O:P></P>=0A<P cl=
ass=3DMsoNormal>They developed spaceflight relatively quickly, bu=
t found no other sentient life near them.<SPAN style=3D"mso-space=
run: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Over the centuries, they developed the be=
lief that theirs was the only race in existance.<SPAN style=3D"ms=
o-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>As they ventured further into the g=
alaxy, they did finally encounter other species. </P>=0A<P class=3D=
MsoNormal><O:P></O:P></P>=0A<P class=3DMsoNormal>Unfortunately th=
eir isolation had already left them strongly xenophobic.</P>=0A<P=
 class=3DMsoNormal>Their prefered weapons are Railguns and Missil=
es.</P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>=0A<P class=3DMsoNormal><SPAN st=
